headline.print_headline: Marussia Make It to the Test-After a Breakdown
headline.main: Marussia Make It to the Test-After a Breakdown

lead_paragraph: While some Formula One teams struggled to get their 2014 cars working in pre-season testing on Wednesday, tail-enders Marussia suffered a breakdown before they had even got theirs to the Jerez circuit.
